<br>
Feneant (the original poster) is level 42.<br>
<br>
More than half of this server is <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> under</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> level 20.<br>
<br>
What do you think that says about the number of people he bumps into during his journeys?<br>
<br>
People are taking their time on FV, and a lot are doing things other than rabidly working to rake in XP.  Just because groups aren't jostling for position in Lower Guk doesn't mean the server is dying.  If you go to any of the lower level zones (commonlands, deserts of ro, Oasis of Marr, Lake of Ill Omen, Highpass Hold, Karanas, etc) you will usually find a quite healthy population of players out and about having fun.<br>
<br>
