<br>
I do, however, agree that we are losing more high level players (30+) and receiving more new players (either new players, second acounts, or re-rolling a new player).  This should be what you are really complaining about - the deminishing high level population.  <br>
<br>
*shrug* there is no really good way to deal with that.  I don't think removing /anon would actually help anything because it is not the difficulty of knowing other's level that is creating group problems.  It is the fact that there is just not enough high level people around the zone you're playing in.  By the time you're 40+, you should at least know a handful of people close to your lvl, and build a solid group from that friend list.<br>
<br>
I don't think we should treat grouping etiquette in the same manner we do in other blue servers.  FV has very different rulesets, and pick up groups just do not work that efficiently in the higher level playgrounds.  In FV, if you want to do a dungeon crawl, it's bring your own group.  If you want an exp grind, it's bring your own group.  If you want to get some item, it's bring your own group.  This phenomena just gets more and more evident as you level up.  I don't think removing /anon would do anything other than giving the beggar a easier time to target the high level players. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uxsatyrx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xsatyrx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 91<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/21/02 6:33:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1151.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The server is dying... slowly but surely</span><hr size=1> hehe...i like Shintou's take on this) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href="http://www.firionavie.org/">Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/fvchat.html" target="_blank"><h3>Chat Room</a></h3></center> <br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.6.1<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  